    "client_msg_id": "fac75425-0806-48cd-844e-ceb9dc5e1996",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "The literature* seems to indicate that the strongest correlation between in-born attribute and high levels of programming ability is <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Working_memory|working memory>. This might suggest that reducing the need for working memory would be one of the best ways to make programming easier for those not \"born to it.\"\n\n(* <https://arxiv.org/pdf/2101.06305.pdf|This paper> and its references would be a good place to start if you're interested in this sort of thing.)",
