    "type": "message",
    "text": "Hey everyone,\nI lead the architecture and UX design for our product at <http://story.ai|story.ai>, and we’re developing a text-oriented low-code platform in alpha-testing. We have two customers we’ve built bespoke automations for using our editor and runtime.\n\n*We would like to help you automate a task that is currently a pain in the butt that you might turn towards something like Zapier for.*\n\nPerhaps your current choice of services have a limitation you can’t get around, and you think it would be possible to fix with a more flexible tool. *We are open to building exactly the integrations you need, even if they are a bit obscure*.\n\nAny help in this regard would be invaluable to validate use-cases for our current product. :heart:\n\nI’m open to answering questions, and if you’re interested in us building you something, DM me :slightly_smiling_face:",
