                "text": ", and we’re developing a text-oriented low-code platform in alpha-testing. We have two customers we’ve built bespoke automations for using our editor and runtime.\n\n"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "We would like to help you automate a task that is currently a pain in the butt that you might turn towards something like Zapier for.",
